Sentencas: Highly dense proton conducting materials of BCZYSZn (BaCe0.8-xZrxY0.15Sm0.05O3-delta (x = 0.15, 0.20) with 4 wt% ZnO as sintering additive), to be used as an intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) electrolyte, have been processed by the conventional solid state reaction method.
Titulo: Highly dense and novel proton conducting materials for SOFC electrolyte

Sentencas: The crystalline phase, microstructure, electrical properties, cell performance and chemical stability of the materials have been investigated.
Titulo: Highly dense and novel proton conducting materials for SOFC electrolyte

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity of BCZYSZn 3 (x = 0.20) material has been measured to be similar to 2.56 x 10(-3) S cm(-1) and similar to 8.32 x 10(-3) S cm(-1) at 600 degrees C and 850 degrees C, respectively in wet 5%H2 in Ar atmosphere.
Titulo: Highly dense and novel proton conducting materials for SOFC electrolyte

Sentencas: Microstructural characterizations of the zinc containing materials (BCZYSZn) show the formation of highly dense morphology with very large grains.
Titulo: Highly dense and novel proton conducting materials for SOFC electrolyte

Sentencas: The chemical stability test of BCZYSZn in pure CO2 shows that the material is very stable up to 1000 degrees C.
Titulo: Highly dense and novel proton conducting materials for SOFC electrolyte

Sentencas: The maximum power density for the BCZYSZn 3 electrolyte cell is found to be 0.42 W/cm(2) at 700 degrees C under the testing atmosphere.
Titulo: Highly dense and novel proton conducting materials for SOFC electrolyte

Sentencas: The performed characterizations reveal that these are suitable proton-conducting candidate materials for efficient electrochemical devices.]
Titulo: Highly dense and novel proton conducting materials for SOFC electrolyte
